                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;14010  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;14011  void watchdog_enable (void) 
0141ba  f04f4080          MOV      r0,#0x40000000
;;;14012  {
;;;14013  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;

;;;14015  LPC_WDT->WDMOD=3;

0141cc  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
;;;14016  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;

;;;14017  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;

0141d8  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14018  }
0141da  4770              BX       lr
;;;14019  
                          ENDP

                          ENDP
